This paper is about a system architecture for distributed network measurements, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the use of web services and SOA, which are related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses security measures to protect against malicious users, which is related to computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper mentions the use of a public database to store measurement results, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
